sume%20it%2C%20said%20Mr%20Joshi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20whole%20country%20is%20cheering%2C%20they%20want%20Air%20India%20to%20do%20well.%20All%20these%20emotions%20put%20together%20took%20us%20towards%20the%20direction%20that%20it%20must%20have%20a%20touch%20of%20legacy%20and%20at%20the%20same%20time%20look%20towards%20the%20future%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20clarified%20that%20the%20Maharaja%20mascot%20remains%20a%20part%20of%20Air%20India%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20Maharaja%20will%20live%20on%2C%20it%20will%20remain%20beloved.%20But%20his%20look%20is%20being%20changed.%20The%20purple%20and%20gold%20colors%20are%20being%20added%20to%20his%20look.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20buzz%20over%20a%20possible%20Maharani%20mascot%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BEverything%20can't%20be%20revealed%20at%20this%20moment.%20Wait%20and%20you'll%20see%20how%20it%20evolves.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20livery%20and%20the%20new%20design%20feature%20a%20palette%20of%20deep%20red%2C%20aubergine%2C%20and%20gold%20highlights%2C%20as%20well%20as%20a%20chakra-inspired%20pattern.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAir%20India%20CEO%20Campbell%20Wilson%20has%20called%20the%20rebranding%20a%20%26quot%3Btotal%20and%20complete%26quot%3B%20transformation%20of%20the%20airline.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20not%20just%20changing%20the%20brand.%20It%20is%20a%20big%20project.%20There%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20moving%20parts.%20But%20we're%20absolutely%20committed%20to%20the%20transformation%20of%20Air%20India.%20We're%20investing%20a%20lot%20of%20money%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20time%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20passion%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFlyers%20will%20get%20to%20see%20the%20new%20logo%20by%20December%20end%20when%20Air%20India's%20first%20Airbus%20A350%20enters%20its%20fleet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETasneem%20Ali%2C%20who%20designed%20the%20new%20logo%20for%20Air%20India%2C%20said%20they%20wanted%20to%20create%20something%20that's%20%26