e%20success%20wherein%20crores%20of%20households%20hoisted%20the%20'Tiranga'%20at%20their%20homes%20physically%20and%20six%20crore%20people%20uploaded%20selfies%20on%20'Har%20Ghar%20Tiranga'%20website%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20year%2C%20India%20Post%20is%20selling%20and%20facilitating%20the%20national%20flag%20through%20its%201.6%20lakh%20post%20offices%20to%20celebrate%20'Har%20Ghar%20Tiranga'%20campaign%2C%20the%20government%20said%20earlier.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20had%20also%20urged%20citizens%20last%20year%20to%20use%20'Tiranga'%20as%20their%20profile%20picture%20on%20social%20media%20accounts%20between%20August%202%20and%20August%2015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20Indian%20citizens%20were%20not%20allowed%20to%20hoist%20the%20National%20Flag%20except%20on%20selected%20occasions.%20This%20changed%20after%20a%20decade-long%20legal%20battle%20by%20industrialist%20Naveen%20Jindal%20culminated%20in%20the%20landmark%20Supreme%20Court%20judgement%20of%20January%2023%2C%202004%2C%20that%20declared%20that%20the%20right%20to%20fly%20the%20National%20Flag%20freely%20with%20respect%20and%20dignity%20is%20a%20fundamental%20right%20of%20an%20Indian%20citizen%20within%20the%20meaning%20of%20Article%2019(1)%20(a)%20of%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691727960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fit2qmk1g_har-ghar-tiranga-campaign_625x300_11_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhar-ghar-tiranga-campaign-independence-day-2023-har-ghar-tiranga-2-0-launched-with-a-bike-rally-of-mps-in-delhi-4288495%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20campaign%2C%20in%20which%20people%20will%20be%20encouraged%20to%20hoist%20the%20national%20flag%20at%20their%20homes%2C%20will%20be%20celebrated%20across%20the%20country%20from%20August%2013%20to%20August%2015%2C%20as%20part%20of%20the%20%26quot%3BAzadi%20Ka%20Amrit%20Mahotsav%26quot%3B.%2