pheld%20the%20high%20court%E2%80%99s%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691727951000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F15184329%2F20230103_124657.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fcourt-tells-asi-stakeholders-not-to-give-media-unofficial-info-on-gyanvapi-mosque-survey%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Judge%20A.K.%20Vishvesha%20allowed%20an%20application%20moved%20by%20the%20Anjuman%20Intezamia%20Masjid%20Committee%2C%20which%20said%20that%20though%20the%20ASI%20has%20not%20issued%20any%20statements%20regarding%20the%20survey%2C%20incorrect%20and%20untrue%20information%20is%20being%20disseminated%20haphazardly%20across%20social%2C%20print%20and%20electronic%20media.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fcourt-tells-asi-stakeholders-not-to-give-media-unofficial-info-on-gyanvapi-mosque-survey%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Jailer'%20box%20office%20collection%20day%201%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691727919000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-102633126%2Cimgsize-29054.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Ftamil%2Fmovies%2Fbox-office%2Fjailer-box-office-collection-day-1-rajinikanth-starrer-mints-over-rs-72-crores-on-a-working-day%2Farticleshow%2F102633126.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F102633126.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ERajinikanth's%20'Jailer'%20has%20hit%20the%20big%20screens%20and%20the%20film%20has%20been%20receiving%20a%20positive%20response%20all%20over.%20The%20opening%20day%20box%20office%20collection%20of%20the%20film%20is%20out%20now%2C%20and%20the%20film%20has%20reportedly%20earned%20over%20Rs%2072%20crores%20worlwide.%20'Jailer'%20has%20become%20the%20highest%20Tamil%20opening%20of%202023%20by%20surpassing%20Mani%20Ratnam's%20'Ponniyin%20Selvan%202'.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Ftamil%2Fmovies%2Fbox-office%2Fjailer-box-office-collection-day-1-rajinikanth-starrer-mints-over-rs-72-crores-on-a-working-day%2Farticleshow%2F102633126.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Doctors%20Can%20Now%20Refuse%20To%20Treat%20%5C%22Abusive%2C%20Violent%5C%22%20Patients%3A%20Medical%20Body%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDoctors%20can%20now%20refuse%20to%20treat%20%26quot%3Babusive%2C%20unruly%2C%20and%20violent%20patients%20or%20relatives%26quot%3B%2C%C2%A0the%20National%20Medical%20Commission%20Registered%20Medical%20Practioner%20said%2C%20taking%C2%A0a%20major%20step%20toward%20curbing%20the%20ongoing%20instances%20of%20violence%20against%20medical%20practitioners.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20RMP%20who%20attends%20to%20the%20patient%20will%20be%20fully%20accountable%20for%20his%20actions%20and%20entitled%20to%20the%20appropriate%20fees.%20In%20case%20of%20abusive%2C%20unruly%2C%20and%20violent%20patients%20or%20relatives%2C%20the%20RMP%20can%20document%20and%20report%20the%20behavior%20and%20refuse%20to%20treat%20the%20patient.%20Such%20patients%20should%20be%20referred%20for%20further%20treatment%20elsewhere%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20notification%20mentioned%20under%20the%20duties%20of%20RMPs%20towards%20their%20patients%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20new%20regulations%20will%20replace%20the%20Medical%20Council%20of%20India's%20(MCI)%20Code%20of%20Medical%20Ethics%202002.%20This%20is%20for%20the%20first%20time%20that%20doctors%20will%20have%20the%20right%20to%20refusal%20of%20patient%20treatment%20to%20unruly%20and%20violent%20patients.%20The%20move%20is%20aimed%20at%20discouraging%20violence%20against%20doctors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRMP%20is%20free%20to%20choose%20whom%20he%20will%20serve%2C%20except%20in%20case%20of%20a%20life-threatening%20emergency.%20Having%20accepted%20a%20case%2C%20the%20RMP%20should%20neither%20neglect%20the%20patient%20nor%20withdraw%20from%20the%20case%20without%20giving%20adequate%20notice%20to%20the%20patient%20and%20his%20family.%20If%20a%20change%20of%20RMP%20is%20needed%20(for%20example%2C%20the%20patient%20needs%20a%20procedure%20done%20by%20another%20RMP)%2C%20consent%20should%20be%20obtained%20from%20the%20patient%20himself%20or%20the%20guardian.%20The%20RMP%20who%20attends%20to%20the%20patient%20will%20be%20fully%20accountable%20for%20his%20actions%20and%20entitled%20to%20the%20appropriate%20fees%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20notification%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt's%20also%20mentioned%20in%20the%20notification%20under%20duties%20of%20RMPs%20towards%20the%20public%20and%20allied%20healthcare%20professionals%20that%20doctors%20can't%20receive%20any%20gifts%2C%20travel%20facilities%20etc%20from%20pharmaceutical%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRMPs%20and%20their%20families%20must%20not%20receive%20any%20gifts%2C%20travel%20facilities%2C%20hospitality%2C%20cash%20or%20monetary%20grants%2C%20consultancy%20fee%20or%20honorariums%2C%20or%20access%20to%20entertainment%20or%20recreation%20from%20pharmaceutical%20companies%20or%20their%20representatives%2C%20commercial%20healthcare%20establishments%2C%20medical%20device%20companies%2C%20or%20corporate%20hospitals%20under%20any%20pretext%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20this%20does%20not%20include%20salaries%20and%20benefits%20that%20RMPs%20may%20receive%20as%20employees%20of%20these%20organisations%2C%20the%20regulations%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20the%20regulations%20said%2C%20RMPs%20should%20not%20be%20involved%20in%20any%20third-party%20educational%20activity%20like%20CPD%2C%20seminar%2C%20workshop%2C%20symposia%2C%20conference%2C%20etc.%2C%20which%20involves%20direct%20or%20indirect%20sponsorships%20from%20pharmaceutical%20companies%20or%20the%20allied%20health%20sector.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20Right%20to%20remuneration%20of%20RMP%20it's%20mentioned%20in%20the%20notification%20that%20the%20consultation%20fees%20should%20be%20made%20known%20to%20the%20patient%20before%20examination%20or%20treatment%20of%20the%20patient.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20reasonable%20estimation%20of%20the%20cost%20of%20surgery%20or%20treatment%20should%20be%20provided%20to%20the%20patient%20to%20enable%20an%20informed%20decision.%20RMP%20can%20refuse%20to%20treat%20or%20to%20continue%20to%20treat%20a%20patient%20if%20the%20fees%2C%20as%20indicated%2C%20are%20not%20paid%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691727840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-02%2Fj3nulf8_medical-student-generic-medicine-generic-doctor-generic_625x300_25_February_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdoctors-can-refuse-treatment-to-violent-abusive-patients-medical-body-4288536%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Doctors%20can%20now%20refuse%20to%20treat%20%26quot%3Babusive%2C%20unruly%2C%20and%20violent%20patients%20or%20relatives%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20National%20Medical%20Commission%20Registered%20Medical%20Practioner%20said%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdoctors-can-refuse-treatment-to-violent-abusive-patients-medical-body-4288536%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdoctors-can-refuse-treatment-to-violent-abusive-patients-medical-body-4288536%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdoctors-can-refuse-treatment-to