%20khaps%2C%20farmer%20unions%2C%20and%20religious%20leaders%20from%20Haryana%20held%20a%20'Mahapanchayat'%20in%20Hisar%20to%20condemn%20the%20violence%20and%20passed%20several%20resolutions%20calling%20for%20peace%20and%20harmony%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20mahapanchayat%2C%20organised%20by%20the%20Bhartiya%20Kisan%20Mazdoor%20Union%2C%20was%20attended%20by%20Hindus%2C%20Muslims%2C%20and%20Sikhs.%20The%20meeting%20resolved%20that%20people%20from%20all%20religions%20will%20work%20to%20restore%20peace.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20letters%20purportedly%20written%20by%20some%20panchayat%20heads%20in%20Mahendergarh%2C%20Rewari%2C%20and%20Jhajjar%20districts%20surfaced%20online.%20The%20letters%20claim%20that%20the%20panchayats%20have%20banned%20Muslim%20traders%20from%20conducting%20business%20in%20their%20villages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFarm%20unions%20have%20been%20critical%20of%20the%20Haryana%20government's%20handling%20of%20the%20communal%20violence%20in%20Nuh%2C%20while%20khaps%20have%20had%20mixed%20reactions.%20Some%20khaps%20have%20supported%20the%20boycott%20of%20Muslim%20traders%2C%20while%20others%20have%20condemned%20the%20violence%20and%20demanded%20the%20arrest%20of%20Manesar.%20Primarily%2C%20khaps%20related%20to%20the%20Jat%20community%20are%20demanding%20Manesar's%20arrest%20and%20appealing%20for%20communal%20harmony.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManesar%20is%20said%20to%20have%20posted%20a%20video%20on%20social%20media%20in%20which%20he%20claimed%20to%20be%20attending%20the%20Nuh%20religious%20procession%20and%20called%20on%20his%20supporters%20to%20come%20out%20in%20large%20numbers.%20He%20was%20later%20warned%20on%20social%20media%20to%20stay%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManesar%20said%20he%20did%20not%20attend%20the%20gathering%20at%20the%20advice%20of%20the%20Vishwa%20Hindu%20Parishad%2C%20which%20feared%20that%20his%20presence%20would%20create%20tensions%20in%20the%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20special%20investigation%20team%20(SIT)%20will%20be%20formed%20to%20investigate%20the%20role%20of%20Manesar%20in%20the%20clashes%2C%20said%20Haryana%20state%20police%20chief%20P%20K%20Agrawal%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2030-year-old%20is%20wanted%20by%20the%20police%20for%20the%20kidnapping%20and%20murder%20of%20two%20Muslim%20men%20found%20dead%20in%20a%20burnt%20car%20in%20Bhiwani%20in%20February.%20The%20bodies%20of%20two%20cattle%20traders%2C%20Junaid%20and%20Nasir%2C%20were%20found%20burnt%20in%20a%20car.%20Their%20families%20in%20Rajasthan's%20Bharatpur%20alleged%20that%20they%20were%20beaten%20and%20killed%20by%20members%20of%20the%20Bajrang%20Dal%2C%20but%20the%20group%20has%20denied%20any%20involvement%20in%20the%20crime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESchools%20and%20transportation%20services%20in%20Nuh%20will%20reopen%20today%20after%20being%20closed%20for%20two%20weeks%20following%20the%20communal%20violence.%20Authorities%20have%20also%20urged%20Muslim%20clerics%20to%20offer%20Friday%20prayers%20at%20their%20homes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20view%20of%20the%20normal%20situation%20in%20the%20area%2C%20it%20has%20been%20decided%20to%20open%20all%20educational%20institutions%20from%20August%2011.%20Similarly%2C%20bus%20services%20of%20Haryana%20State%20Transport%20are%20also%20being%20fully%20restored%20from%20August%2011.%20Curfew%20will%20be%20relaxed%20on%20Friday.%20ATMs%20in%20the%20municipal%20corporation%20area%20of%20Nuh%2C%20Tawdu%2C%20Punhana%2C%20Ferozepur%20Jhirka%20and%20Pingawa%20and%20Nagina%20blocks%20will%20remain%20open%20during%20the%20relaxation%20period%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20statement%20from%20the%20Nuh%20administration%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691723280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Frh2ui1k_nuh-_625x300_11_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fharyana-nuh-violence-live-haryana-khaps-farmer-unions-demand-monu-manesars-arrest-call-for-peace-4288436%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Days%20after%20the%20communal%20clashes%20in%20Haryana's%20Nuh%2C%20several%20farmer%20unions%20and%20Khap%20panchayats%20have%20appealed%20for%20peace%20and%20demanded%20the%20arrest%20of%20cow%20vigilante%20Monu%20Manesar.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A60%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fharyana-nuh-violence-live-haryana-khaps-farmer-unions-demand-monu-manesars-arrest-call-for-peace-4288436%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fharyana-nuh-violence-live-haryana-khaps-farmer-unions-demand-monu-manesars-arrest-call-for-peace-4288436%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fharyana-nuh-violence-live-haryana-khaps-farmer-unions-demand-monu-manesars-arrest-call-for-peace-4288436%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Analysts%20Fed%20on%20Government%20Spin%20Demand%20Facts%20From%20Rahul%20Gandhi%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F11083115%2FScreenshot-2023-08-11-at-8.30.51-AM.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20political%20analysts%20and%20newspaper%20editorials%20have%20criticised%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20for%20not%20making%20a%20hard%2C%20factual%20presentation%20in%20the%20no-confidence%20debate%20on%20the%20Manipur%20issue%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%20At%20the%20outset%2C%20Rahul%20said%20he%20would%20speak%20from%20the%20heart%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Frahul-gandhi-parliament-bharat-mata-manipur%5C%22%3Elaunched%20a%20scathing%20attack%20on%20Modi%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20likening%20him%20to%20Ravana%2C%20who%20perished%20because%20of%20his%20own%20arrogance.%20He%20charged%20the%20Centre%20with%20murdering%20Bharat%20Mata%20in%20Manipur.%20He%20also%20launched%20a%20wider%20attack%20on%20the%20BJP%20for%20using%20kerosene%20to%20spark%20divisive%20fires%20in%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20country%20like%20Haryana%2C%20which%20is%20engulfed%20in%20communal%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGandhi%20was%20clearly%20trying%20to%20set%20a%20larger%20narrative%20about%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20politics.%20He%20deliberately%20stayed%20away%20from%20a%20detailed%20questioning%20of%20the%20government%20actions%20or%20lack%20of%20it%20in%20Manipur.%20Some%20analysts%20have%20compared%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%2037-minute%20speech%20with%20Union%20home%20minister%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Famit-shah-defends-biren-singh-in-parliament%5C%22%3EAmit%20Shah%E2%80%99s%20speech%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20over%20two%20hours%2C%20in%20which%20he%20gave%20a%20factual%20presentation%20on%20the%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20overall%20governance%20record.%20Of%20course%2C%20Shah%20didn%E2%80%99t%20express%20any%20regret%20that%20his%20government%2C%20both%20at%20the%20Centre%20and%20in%20the%20state%2C%20had%20totally%20failed%20to%20control%20prolonged%20violence%20and%20civil%20war%20in%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20irony%20here%20is%20that%20the%20BJP%20under%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20Shah%20has%20shown%20scant%20regard%20for%20facts%20and%20data%20over%20the%20last%20nine%20years%2C%20and%20have%20largely%20relied%20on%20toxic%20narrative-building%20based%20on%20the%20Hindutva%20ideology.%20Yet%2C%20political%20analysts%20were%20praising%20the%20home%20minister%20for%20a%20%E2%80%9Cfactual%E2%80%9D%20presentation%20of%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20nine%20years%20in%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20expect%20the%20Opposition%20to%20stick%20to%20facts%20when%20the%20ruling%20party%E2%80%99s%20standard%20playbook%20is%20to%20feed%20its%20majoritarian%C2%A0%20narrative%20relentlessly%2C%20on%20a%20daily%20basis%2C%20is%20a%20bit%20rich.%20Rahul%20tried%20to%20set%20a%20counter%20narrative%2C%20straight%20from%20the%20heart%2C%20by%20talking%20about%20the%20death%20of%20Bharat%20Mata%20in%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flink.sbstck.com%2