lised%20that%20the%20Modi%20regime%20has%20no%20respect%20for%20facts%20or%20data%2C%20and%20will%20seek%20to%20convert%20every%20situation%20to%20its%20advantage%2C%20based%20on%20its%20deeply%20divisive%20reflexes.%20Manipur%20and%20Haryana%20are%20just%20the%20two%20most%20recent%20examples.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Parliament%20Diary%3A%20Parts%20of%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20Speech%20Expunged%20and%20Missing%20Sansad%20TV%20Camera%20Angles%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fparliament-diary-parts-of-rahul-gandhis-speech-expunged-and-missing-sansad-tv-camera-angles%5C%22%3EParts%20of%20Rahul%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20Speech%20Expunged%20and%20Missing%20Sansad%20TV%20Camera%20Angles%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20it%20is%20really%20futile%20to%20expect%20the%20opposition%20to%20wade%20through%20myriad%20factual%20details%20when%20the%20other%20side%20is%20playing%20some%20other%20game%20altogether.%20On%20the%20contrary%2C%C2%A0%20a%20broader%20counter-narrative%20strategy%20deriving%20from%20the%20basic%20framework%20from%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%20may%20be%20the%20urgent%20need%20of%20the%20hour.%20Which%20is%20what%20Rahul%20was%20attempting.%20The%20fact%20that%20Sansad%20TV%20camera%20chose%20to%20focus%20on%20Rahul%20only%2040%25%20of%20the%20time%20during%20his%20speech%20%2C%20as%20opposed%20to%20near%20total%20focus%20on%20Shah%20during%20his%20address%2C%20shows%20the%20nervousness%20of%20the%20ruling%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20any%20case%2C%20listening%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnarendra-modi-parliament-speech-manipur%5C%22%3EModi%E2%80%99s%20response%20in%20the%20House%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20it%20would%20seem%20Rahul%20was%20right%20in%20resorting%20to%20a%20broader%20narrative%20of%20the%20BJP%20as%20an%20%E2%80%98enemy%20of%20Bharat%20Mata%E2%80%99%20because%20even%20Modi%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20dealt%20with%20facts%20or%20details%20of%20anything.%20He%20is%20also%20building%20a%20broader%20narrative.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20prime%20minister%20clearly%20tried%20to%20portray%20the%20opposition%20parties%20as%20anti-India%20and%20a%20group%20in%20whom%20the%20people%20had%20no%20confidence%20left.%20Modi%20said%20India%20had%20entered%20a%20golden%20period%20under%20the%20BJP%20rule%20and%20this%20would%20%E2%80%9Clay%20the%20foundation%20for%20a%201%2C000%20years%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20glory%E2%80%9D.%20Such%20hyperbole%20has%20little%20to%20do%20with%20facts%20on%20the%20ground.%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20was%20an%20election%20speech%20for%20the%20most%20part%20when%20people%20expected%20him%20to%20say%20something%20substantive%20on%20Manipur%20violence.%20In%20some%20ways%2C%20Rahul%20might%20have%20anticipated%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20he%20was%20probably%20right%20in%20pre-empting%20Modi%20with%20his%20sharp%20and%20focused%20attack%20on%20the%20BJP%20as%20having%20%E2%80%9Cmurdered%20Bharat%20Mata%20in%20Manipur%E2%80%9D.%20His%20charge%20that%20the%20BJP%20under%20Modi%20was%20throwing%20kerosene%20and%20setting%20fire%20to%20different%20parts%20of%20India%20with%20its%20divisive%20politics%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20a%20theme%20for%20the%20Congress%20in%20the%202024%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691722920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F11083115%2FScreenshot-2023-08-11-at-8.30.51-AM.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fanalysts-fed-on-government-spin-demand-facts-from-rahul-gandhi%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22To%20expect%20the%20Opposition%20to%20stick%20to%20facts%20when%20the%20ruling%20party%E2%80%99s%20standard%20playbook%20is%20to%20feed%20its%20majoritarian%C2%A0%20narrative%20relentlessly%2C%20on%20a%20daily%20basis%2C%20is%20a%20bit%20rich.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fanalysts-fed-on-government-spin-deman