riumph%20once%2C%20he%20hasn't%20won%20the%20ODI%20World%20Cup%20yet%2C%20be%20it%20as%20a%20captain%20or%20as%20a%20player.%20Having%20been%20given%20the%20captaincy%20of%20the%20Indian%20team%20after%20Virat%20Kohli's%20exit%20from%20the%20leadership%20role%2C%20Rohit%20is%20eager%20to%20bring%20the%20Team%20success%20on%20all%20fronts.%20However%2C%20'captaincy'%20still%20remains%20secorndary%20for%20him%2C%20it's%20his%20role%20as%20a%20batter%20that%20is%20primary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20have%20gone%20without%20a%20trophy%20in%20ICC%20events%20for%20a%20decade%20now%2C%20with%20their%20last%20major%20win%20coming%20in%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%202013%2C%20two%20years%20after%20their%20World%20Cup%20triumph%20at%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHonestly%2C%20I%20have%20never%20won%20a%20(50%20overs)%20World%20Cup%2C%20it's%20a%20dream%20to%20win%20a%20World%20Cup%20and%20to%20be%20here%20fighting%20for%20it%20nothing%20makes%20me%20happier%20than%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Rohit%20told%20the%20media%20here%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20an%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20don't%20get%20World%20Cups%20on%20a%20platter%2C%20you%20have%20to%20really%20work%20hard%20and%20that%20is%20what%20we%20have%20been%20doing%20all%20these%20years%20from%202011%20till%20now%20we%20all%20are%20fighting%20for%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20India%20captain%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEveryone%20is%20desperate%20to%20go%20and%20win%2C%20because%20we%20know%20we%20have%20a%20good%20team.%20We%20are%20all%20good%20players%2C%20that%20inner%20confidence%20and%20self-belief%20is%20there%20that%20they%20can%20do%20it.%20It's%20not%20happened%20doesn't%20mean%20that%20we%20take%20it%20lightly.%20When%20we%20lost%20the%202022%20World%20Cup%2C%20I%20said%20we%20will%20keep%20fighting%20for%20the%20next%20World%20Cup%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20World%20Test%20Championship%20was%20coming%20and%20I%20said%20we%20will%20keep%20fighting%20for%20it%2C%20no%20matter%20what.%20Kabhi%20na%20kabhi%20to%20milega%20(we%20will%20win%20it%20at%20some%20point)%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20expressed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERohit%20said%20while%20he%20is%20tasked%20to%20lead%20the%20team%2C%20his%20primary%20job%20is%20to%20do%20well%20as%20a%20batter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20need%20to%20do%20first%20as%20a%20batter.%20Captaincy%20is%20secondary...%20my%20role%20in%20the%20team%20is%20more%20as%20a%20batter.%20Obviously%20to%20captain%20well%20as%20well%2C%20(but)%20first%20of%20all%2C%20I%20have%20to%20score%20big%20runs%20and%20win%20games%20for%20the%20team.%26quot%3B%20With%20key%20men%20such%20as%20KL%20Rahul%20and%20Shreyas%20Iyer%20unavailable%20in%20the%20lead-up%20to%20the%20World%20Cup%2C%20Rohit%20said%20he%20is%20scared%20of%20injuries%20now%20but%20stressed%20on%20the%20importance%20of%20resting%20the%20players.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLast%20year%20also%20we%20did%20the%20same%20thing%20%E2%80%94%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%20was%20there%2C%20so%20we%20didn't%20play%20one-day%20cricket.%20Now%20also%20we%20are%20doing%20the%20same%2C%20the%20ODI%20World%20Cup%20is%20there%2C%20so%20we%20are%20not%20playing%20T20s%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can't%20play%20everything%20and%20be%20ready%20for%20the%20World%20Cup.%20We%20decided%20this%20two%20years%20ago.%20(Ravindra)%20Jadeja%20is%20also%20not%20playing%20T20%2C%20you%20did%20not%20ask%20about%20him%3F%20I%20understand%20about%20the%20focus%20(on%20himself%20and%20Virat).%20But%20Jadeja%20is%20also%20not%20playing%2C%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERohit%20said%20in%20reply%20to%20a%20query%20about%20him%20and%20Kohli%20missing%20India's%20recent%20T20%20assignments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20World%20Cup%20year%3B%20we%20want%20to%20keep%20everyone%20fresh%3B%20already%20we%20had%20so%20many%20injuries%20in%20the%20team%20that%20I%20am%20scared%20of%20injuries%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERohit%20revealed%20that%20the%20team%20management%20had%20a%20discussion%20with%20the%20BCCI%20on%20the%20aspect%20of%20managing%20the%20workload%20of%20players.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20had%20a%20discussion%20with%20the%20BCCI%20also%20that%20we%20need%20to%20look%20after%20the%20players%20well.%20Whenever%20we%20have%20an%20opportunity%20to%20rest%20players%2C%20we%20will%20rest%20players%20and%20rotate%20them.%20We%20don't%20want%20anyone%20to%20miss%20the%20key%20events.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20couple%20of%20our%20key%20players%20missed%20some%20big%20events%20in%20the%20last%20two%20years%20and%20we%20don't%20want%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3EWith%20PTI%20inputs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691722440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fd31t9bk_rohit-pc_650x300_12_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fcaptaincy-is-secondary-my-role-is-rohit-sharmas-honest-admission-4287022%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%20captain%20Rohit%20Sharma%20admitted%20that%20'captaincy'%20is%20his%20secondary%20role%20in%20the%20national%20team%20at%20the%20moment.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A31%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fcaptaincy-is-secondary-my-role-is-rohit-sharmas-honest-admission-4287022%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fcaptaincy-is-secondary-my-role-is-rohit-sharmas-honest-admission-4287022%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fcaptaincy-is-secondary-my-role-is-rohit-sharmas-honest-admission-4287022%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Review%3A%20Akshay's%20OMG%202%20Is%20Buoyed%20By%20Lively%20Performances%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20video%20of%20a%20boy%20pleasuring%20himself%20in%20the%20school%20toilet%20goes%20viral.%20He%20is%20rusticated%20for%20aberrant%20behaviour.%20He%20is%20gripped%20by%20self-loathing%2C%20his%20father%20is%20livid%20with%20him%20and%20their%20self-righteous%20neighbours%20sever%20all%20links%20with%20the%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20boy's%20father%2C%20an%20unswerving%20devotee%20of%20Lord%20Shiva%2C%20decides%20to%20leave%20the%20central%20Indian%20holy%20town%20they%20call%20home.%20But%20before%20the%20family%20can%20board%20the%20train%20that%20will%20take%20them%20to%20Saharanpur%2C%20an%20emissary%20of%20Lord%20Shiva%20shows%20up.%20The%20simple-minded%20man%20witnesses%20a%20miracle.%20He%20returns%20home%20and%20opts%20to%20stay%20and%20fight.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKanti%20Sharan%20Mudgal%20(Pankaj%20Tripathi)%20takes%20the%20school%20to%20court%20and%20demands%20that%20his%20son's%20unjustified%20rustication%20be%20revoked.%20By%20bringing%20matters%20out%20in%20the%20open%2C%20he%20hopes%20to%20help%20the%20cowering%20boy%20rid%20himself%20of%20his%20sense%20of%20guilt%20and%20shame%20and%20compel%20the%20institution%20to%20accept%20the%20blame%20for%20not%20giving%20him%20and%20his%20classmates%20the%20guidance%20that%20they%20needed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20purpose%20of%20Kanti's%20petition%20-%20no%20lawyer%20is%20willing%20to%20represent%20him%20so%20he%20becomes%20his%20own%20counsel%20-%20is%20to%20impress%20upon%20the%20court%20the%20need%20to%20introduce%20a%20comprehensive%20sex%20education%20course%20in%20schools%20so%20that%20boys%20of%20his%20son's%20ilk%20(and%20girls%2C%20too)%20do%20not%20fall%20prey%20to%20misconceptions%20about%20their%20bodies%20and%20sexual%20desires.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%2C%20in%20a%20nutshell%2C%20is%20what%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fat-omg-2-screening-yami-gautam-fatima-sana-shaikh-aahana-kumra-and-others-marked-their-presence-4288069%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3EOMG%202%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20written%20and%20directed%20by%20Amit%20Rai%20(he%20made%20Road%20to%20Sangam%2013%20years%20ago)%2C%20is%20about.%20At%20one%20level%2C%20the%20film%20may%20be%20deemed%20a%20pertinent%20courtroom%20drama%20that%20engages%20in%20a%20conversation%20of%20import.%20It%2C%20however%2C%20frequently%20ties%20itself%20up%20in%20knots%20and%20that%20isn't%20a%20pretty%20sight.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20overlong%2C%20convoluted%20and%20simplistic%20satire%20-%20the%20sprinkling%20of%20comedy%20strewn%20across%20it%20renders%20the%20exercise%20more%20flippant%20than%20funny%20-%20ultimately%20yields%20no%20more%20than%20a%20sloppy%20mish-mash%20of%20the%20relevant%20and%20the%20gratuitous%20that%20even%20the%20most%20omnipotent%20of%20gods%20cannot%20salvage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGod's%20messenger%20in%20%3Ci%3EOMG%20%3C%2Fi%3E%20is%20embodied%20by%20a%20flamboyant%20Akshay%20Kumar.%20The%20star's%20presence%20in%20the%20film%20is%20understandable.%20It%20enhances%20the%20box-office%20potential%20of%20the%20venture.%20But%20why%20Kanti%20Sharan%20Mudgal%20would%20need%20divine%20intervention%20to%20sort%20out%20his%20and%20his%20son's%20everyday%20problems%20in%20the%20real%20world%20is%20never%20clearly%20and%20convincingly%20established.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20almost%20as%20if%20the%20makers%20had%20a%20narrative%20kernel%20in%20place%20and%20were%20then%20given%20access%20to%20the%20title%20of%20a%20commercially%20successful%20film%20from%20a%20decade%20ago.%20God%20had%20to%20be%20willy-nilly%20made%20a%20part%20of%20the%20deal%2C%20no%20matter%20how%20tangentially%2C%20for%20the%20film%20to%20be%20called%20%3Ci%3EOMG%202%3C%2Fi%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20return%20to%20the%20yarn%2C%20the%20exuberant%20godly%20mediator%20in%20a%20town%20whose%20reigning%20deity%20is%20Shiva%20is%20followed%20by%20a%20colourfully%20draped%20bull%20-%20presumably%20a%20live%20incarnation%20of%20Nandi%20-%20every%20time%20he%20exits%20a%20scene%20after%20having%20trotted%20out%20useful%20maxims%20for%20the%20benefit%20of%20a%20confused%20believer.%20But%20the%20rockstar%20problem-solver%20seems%20to%20enjoy%20nothing%20more%20than%20getting%20behind%20the%20wheel%20of%20a%20snazzy%20car%20and%20driving%20like%20a%20maniac.%20Traffic%20rules%20obviously%20do%20not%20apply%20to%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20scene%20late%20in%20the%20film%2C%20he%20performs%20another%20life-saving%20miracle.%20The%20magical%20deed%20done%2C%20he%20takes%20Kanti%20for%20a%20spin%20in%20a%20fast%20car%20that%20leaves%20the%20latter%20dizzy%20with%20a%20mix%20of%20alarm%20and%20excitement.%20But%20none%20of%20the%20exhilaration%20that%20he%20feels%20is%20transmitted%20to%20the%20audience%20as%20the%20film%20limps%20towards%20a%20predictable%20climax.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FY6ZKXqM7HNQ%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20%3Cem%3EOMG%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20released%20in%202012%2C%20an%20agnostic%20shopkeeper%20sues%20the%20Almighty%20when%20his%20curio%20store%20is%20destroyed%20in%20an%20earthquake%2C%20which%20his%20insurance%20company%20defines%20as%20%26quot%3Ban%20act%20of%20God%26quot%3B.%20The%20film%2C%20which%20had%20Akshay%20Kumar%20in%20the%20role%20of%20an%20avatar%20of%20Lord%20Krishna%2C%20revolved%20around%20a%20courtroom%20debate%20between%20faith%20and%20rationalism%2C%20between%20belief%20and%20scorn.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20completely%20unrelated%20follow-up%20to%20that%20film%2C%20there%20is%20no%20room%20for%20the%20power%20of%20the%20divine%20to%20be%20called%20into%20question.%20Fervour%20replaces%20logic%20as%20God%20assumes%20a%20human%20form%20and%20descends%20on%20earth%20on%20a%20mission.%20He%20arms%20a%20harried%20father%20with%20the%20courage%2C%20and%20ammunition%2C%20to%20take%20on%20a%20powerful%20school%20and%20a%20bunch%20of%20businesses%20that%20give%20teenagers%20the%20false%20hope%20that%20there%20are%20quick-fixes%20available%20for%20their%20sexual%20deficiencies%2C%20real%20or%20imagined.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOMG%202%2C%20which%20endorses%20blind%20faith%20even%20as%20it%20trots%20out%20arguments%20in%20favour%20of%20adopting%20a%20scientific%2C%20clinical%20approach%20to%20sex%20education%20in%20schools%2C%20goes%20round%20in%20circles%20as%20it%20pits%20Kanti%20against%20Kamini%20Maheshwari%20(Yami%20Gautam%20Dhar)%2C%20a%20lawyer%20who%20has%20a%20personal%20stake%20in%20the%20outcome%20of%20the%20case.%20She%20is%20the%20daughter-in-law%20(Yami%20Gautam%20Dhar)%200f%20the%20school%20chairman%20(Arun%20Govil).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20plea%20comes%20up%20for%20hearing%20in%20the%20court%20of%20Judge%20Purushottam%20Nagar%20(Pavan%20Raj%20Malhotra)%2C%20an%20amiable%20man%20who%20is%20all%20ears%20to%20Kanti's%20rough%20and%20ready%20arguments%20but%20has%20to%20frequently%20turn%20to%20the%20court%20stenographer%20for%20help%20to%20decipher%20the%20plaintiff's%20earthy%20lingo.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20film%20is%20buoyed%20by%20lively%20performances%20that%20ring%20true%2C%20especially%20the%20ones%20by%20Pankaj%20Tripathi%20and%20Geeta%20Agrawal%2C%20who%20plays%20Kanti's%20befuddled%20and%20emotionally%20rattled%20wife%20Indumati.%20But%20the%20bright%20spots%20go%20abegging%20because%20%3Cem%3EOMG%202%20%3C%2Fem%3Eis%20undermined%20by%20too%20many%20false%20steps%20that%20lead%20it%20astray.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20film%20takes%20a%20random%20potshot%20at%20Macaulay%2C%20talks%20of%20how%20ancient%20India%20was%20a%20model%20of%20modernity%20while%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20world%20was%20stuck%20in%20the%20dark%20ages%20-%20no%20attempt%20is%20made%20to%20provide%20empirical%20evidence%20to%20support%20this%20grand%20theory%20-%20and%20brings%20into%20the%20unduly%20fluffy%20narrative%20allusions%20to%20themes%20(such%20as%20sexual%20violence%2C%20good%20touch%20and%20bad%20touch%2C%20et%20all)%20that%20should%20have%20been%20left%20for%20another%20film.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20makers%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fahead-of-omg-2-release-a-breakdown-of-the-27-changes-in-the-film-4285748%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EOMG%202%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20knew%20where%20to%20draw%20the%20line%20and%20what%20to%20highlight%20and%20what%20to%20weed%20out%2C%20they%20would%20have%20had%20a%20far%20mellower%20and%20infinitely%20more%20convincing%20film%20to%20show%20for%20their%20well-intentioned%20but%20ill-conceived%20efforts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20some%20of%20the%20thoughts%20that%20the%20film%20tosses%20around%20cannot%20be%20faulted%2C%20the%20methods%20that%20it%20employs%20to%20verbalise%20them%20border%20on%20the%20overly%20callow%2C%20when%20they%20are%20not%20outright%20facetious.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20what%20does%20one%20make%20of%20a%20movie%20that%20wants%20to%20say%20the%20right%20things%20but%20does%20not%20quite%20know%20how%20to%20say%20them%3F%20Should%20we%20commend%20it%20for%20just%20trying%3F%20If%20one%20were%20in%20a%20generous%20mood%2C%20the%20answer%20might%20be%20is%20yes%20but%20not%20of%20the%20unequivocal%20kind%20that%20the%20affirmation%20would%20have%20been%20had%20%3Cem%3EOMG%202%3C%2Fem%3E%20not%20been%20such%20an%20exasperatingly%20middling%20affair.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20sum%20up%2C%20%3Cem%3EOMG%202%3C%2Fem%3E%20aspires%20to%20be%20as%20sharp%20as%20a%20scalpel%20but%20is%20actually%20as%20blunt%20as%20the%20back%20of%20a%20knife.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691722320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fceqat55g_omg-2-_625x300_11_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fomg-2-review-akshay-kumars-simplistic-satire-buoyed-by-lively-performances-2-stars-4288424%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22OMG%202%20Review%3A%20God's%20messenger%20is%20embodied%20by%20a%20flamboyant%20Akshay%20Kumar.%20The%20star's%20presence%20is%20understandable.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2