3C%2Fa%3E.%20That%20law%2C%20in%20an%20effort%20to%20help%20combat%20retention%20and%20hiring%20issues%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fs.usda.gov%2Finside-fs%2Fdelivering-mission%2Fexcel%2Fwildland-firefighter-pay-classification-infrastructure-law%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emandated%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20firefighter%20pay%20in%20hard-to-hire%20areas%20would%20increase%20by%20either%20%2420%2C000%20annually%20or%2050%25%20%E2%80%94%20whichever%20is%20less.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20that%20funding%20is%20only%20in%20place%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.govexec.com%2Fpay-benefits%2F2023%2F07%2Fsenate-panel-has-advanced-legislation-avert-wildland-firefighter-pay-cliff%2F388698%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethrough%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20fiscal%20year%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Per%20the%20OMB%2C%20that%20could%20mean%20over%2020%2C000%20firefighters%20could%20see%20pay%20slashed%20in%20October%2C%20with%20some%20making%20as%20little%20as%20%2415%20an%20hour.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20administration%20is%20committed%20to%20building%20a%20more%20robust%20and%20resilient%20wildland%20firefighter%20workforce%20and%20fairly%20compensate%20wildland%20firefighters'%20difficult%20and%20dangerous%20work%20that%20they%20do.%20Each%20firefighter%20has%20put%20their%20lives%20on%20the%20line%20to%20protect%20our%20community%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20senior%20administration%20official%20told%20reporters%20on%20a%20Thursday%20press%20call.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20seen%20bipartisan%20understanding%20of%20the%20need%20to%20provide%20firefighter%20pay%20to%20prevent%20a%20cliff%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20potential%20pay%20cliff%20looms%20amidst%20a%20summer%20of%20deadly%20wildfires%20and%20extreme%20weather.%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnn.com%2Fus%2Flive-news%2Fmaui-wildfires-08-09-23%2Findex.html%5