t%20important%20tech%20innovations.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20sad%20fact%20of%20life%20that%20the%20more%20you%20drive%2C%20the%20more%20danger%20you%20put%20yourself%20in.%20There%20were%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nhtsa.gov%2Fpress-releases%2Ftraffic-crash-death-estimates-2022%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E1.35%20fatalities%20per%20100%20million%20vehicle%20miles%3C%2Fa%3E%20traveled%20in%20the%20US%20in%202022%2C%20according%20to%20the%20National%20Highway%20Traffic%20Safety%20Administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDangerous%20driving%20can%20cost%20lives%2C%20and%20some%20road%20intersections%20are%20known%20to%20be%20more%20perilous%20than%20most.%20But%20technology%20being%20trialed%20on%20a%20controlled-access%20rural%20road%20in%20Virginia%20could%20help%20save%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20been%20developing%20IT%20and%20networking%20infrastructure%20for%20a%20long%20time%2C%20from%202G%20and%203G%20up%20to%205G%2C%26quot%3B%20Masahiko%20Mack%20Nakagawa%2C%20the%20vice%20president%20of%20the%20corporate-business-development%20division%20at%20NEC%2C%20one%20of%20the%20partners%20behind%20the%20Virginia%20project%2C%20told%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20speed%20at%20which%202G%20and%203G%20systems%20operate%20is%20too%20slow%20for%20real-time%20information%20about%20traffic%20flows%20that%20can%20help%20prevent%20collisions%20between%20vehicles%20%E2%80%94%20or%20vehicles%20and%20pedestrians.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E5G%20could%20make%20safer%20roads%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fwhat-frequency-is-5g%5C%22%3Elightning-fast%20speed%20at%20which%205G%20can%20transmit%20data%3C%2Fa%3E%20through%20mobile-internet%20signals%20means%20that%20it's%20possible%20for%20AI%20to%20collect%20data%2C%20analyze%20it%20computationally%2C%20and%20make%20decisions%20based%20on%20that%20analysis%20within%20a%20split%20second%20%E2%80%94%20the%20amount%20of%20time%20it%20takes%20for%20accidents%20to%20happen.%20It's%20possible%20to%20identify%20dangerous%20traffic%20conditions%20or%20hazards%20on%20the%20road%2C%20such%20as%20approaching%20pedestrians%20or%20animals%2C%20and%20warn%20drivers%20to%20take%20evasive%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Virginia%20trial%20involved%20installing%20cameras%20and%20private%205G%20base%20stations%20on%20signal%20poles%20that%20could%20capture%20and%20broadcast%20high-definition%20video%20in%20real%20time%20across%20a%20private%205G%20network%20to%20an%20artificial-intelligence-powered%20analysis%20system%2C%20then%20report%20back%20the%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20a%20car%20is%20approaching%20the%20intersection%2C%20the%20AI%20will%20analyze%20if%20the%20car%20is%20going%20straight%2C%20turning%20right%20or%20turning%20left%2C%20and%20how%20many%20pedestrians%20are%20at%20the%20intersection%2C%26quot%3B%20Nakagawa%20said.%20%26quot%3BOnce%20the%20AI%20decides%20there%20is%20a%20risk%20of%20an%20accident%2C%20the%20system%20will%20broadcast%20information%20to%20the%20pedestrians%20and%20the%20vehicles.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20may%20sound%20like%20science%20fiction%20%E2%80%94%20but%20it's%20fact.%20Trialed%20between%20January%20and%20March%20in%20Blacksburg%2C%20Virginia%2C%20on%20one%20of%20the%20test%20tracks%20that's%20part%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vtti.vt.edu%2Ffacilities%2Fvirginia-smart-roads.html%5C%22%3EVirginia%20Smart%20Roads%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20one%20of%20the%20only%20facilities%20in%20the%20world%20that%20can%20conduct%20these%20advanced%20tests%2C%20the%20system%20analyzed%20video%20in%20real%20time%20using%20AI%20and%20broadcast%20warning%20signals%20to%20vehicles%20and%20pedestrians.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20research%20team%20behind%20the%20project%20suggested%20using%20an%20LED%20light%20mat%20on%20the%20side%20of%20each%20road%20to%20light%20up%20if%20there%20was%20a%20vehicle%20approaching%20to%20prevent%20collisions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20all%2C%2066%20use%20cases%20were%20tested%2C%20including%20motorcycles%2C%20bicycles%2C%20and%20several%20types%20of%20situations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20made%20sure%20that%20in%20all%20those%20use%20cases%2C%20the%20application%20had%20enough%20accuracy%20and%20enough%20performance%2C%26quot%3B%20Nakagawa%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPerformance%2C%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20experiment's%20purposes%2C%20meant%20parsing%20the%20data%20and%20providing%20advice%20in%20a%20short%20enough%20timeframe%20for%20drivers%20to%20prevent%20a%20fatal%20collision.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20team%20behind%20the%20experiment%20set%20a%200.5-second%20limit%20for%20drivers%20to%20be%20notified%20after%20a%20risky%20situation%20arose%2C%20which%20the%20test%20met%20in%20all%20use%20cases.%20That%20time%20limit%2C%20and%20the%20success%20with%20which%20the%20system%20could%20meet%20the%20requirements%2C%20could%20also%20make%20the%205G-enabled%20communications%20tool%20useful%20for%20automated%20driving.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20system%20also%20added%20types%20of%20video%20analytics%20beyond%20traffic%20and%20pedestrian%20monitoring.%20A%20detection%20tool%20for%20unusual%20pedestrian%20behavior%20looks%20to%20see%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20if%20a%20pedestrian%20falls%20down%20and%20doesn't%20move%20at%20the%20intersection%20for%2045%20seconds%3B%20in%20that%20case%2C%20that%20person%20may%20need%20help.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ESafer%2C%20high-tech%20roads%20require%20more%205G%20access%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20important%20because%20too%20many%20people%20fall%20victim%20to%20serious%20or%20fatal%20crashes%20on%20Virginia's%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20nation's%20%E2%80%94%20roads.%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.drivesmartva.org%2Fabout-dsv%2Fannual-report%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20More%20than%201%2C000%20people%20died%20in%202022%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Virginia's%20roadways%2C%20according%20to%20Drive%20Smart%20Virginia%2C%20while%20162%20people%20were%20injured%20every%20single%20day%20because%20of%20vehicle%20crashes%20across%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20project%20comes%20at%20a%20critical%20moment%20for%20Virginia%2C%20whose%20pedestrian%20fatalities%20increased%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.drivesmartva.org%2Fabout-dsv%2Fannual-report%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E37%25%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202022%20over%202021%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EState%20and%20county%20transportation%20departments%20were%20positive%20about%20the%20trial%2C%20Nakagawa%20said.%20The%20Virginia%20Tech%20Transportation%20Institute%20believes%20this%20proof%20of%20concept%20will%20%26quot%3Bimprove%20road%20safety%20by%20informing%20vehicles%20and%20pedestrians%20of%20possible%20traffic%20hazards%20when%20passing%20through%20an%20intersection%2C%26quot%3B%20Mike%20Mollenhauer%2C%20the%20director%20of%20the%20technology-implementation%20division%20at%20the%20institute%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20it's%20unlikely%20to%20stay%20solely%20within%20Virginia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20very%20high%20expectations%20that%20the%205G-enabled%20world%20will%20come%2C%26quot%3B%20Nakagawa%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20see%20a%20lot%20of%20potential%20implementation%20in%20the%20US%20and%20Japan.%20I%20think%20it'll%20take%20three%20to%20five%20years%20for%20the%20implementation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22raw%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F5g-technology-safer-roads-virginia-2023-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691696703000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64c7fe80048ff200190e45e7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F5g-technology-safer-roads-virginia-2023-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%225G-powered%20technology%20