the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmanipur-as-violence-rages-on-mlas-divided-over-whether-or-not-to-hold-special-assembly-session%5C%22%3Eviolence%20hit-state%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20barely%20ten%20minutes%20in%20which%20he%20said%20that%20his%20government%20is%20working%20towards%20peace.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20remaining%20part%20of%20his%20extensive%20speech%20was%20devoted%20to%20attacking%20the%20Congress%2C%20previous%20UPA%20governments%2C%20the%20opposition%20INDIA%20alliance%20and%20the%20developmental%20initiatives%20brought%20to%20the%20North%20East%20in%20the%20nine%20years%20of%20the%20Modi%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20occurred%20despite%20the%20opposition%20saying%20that%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Flok-sabha-debates-no-confidence-motion-even-as-pm-modi-absent%5C%22%3Egoal%20of%20the%20no-confidence%20motion%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20to%20get%20the%20prime%20minister%20to%20address%20the%20ongoing%20violence%20in%20Manipur%20inside%20parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%E2%80%99s%20speech%20saw%20high%20drama%20amid%20loud%20protests%20from%20the%20opposition%2C%20which%20staged%20a%20walkout%20after%201%20hour%20and%2040%20minutes%20of%20the%20speech%20as%20there%20was%20no%20mention%20of%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20Leader%20of%20the%20Congress%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Chowdhury%2C%20was%20suspended%20for%20%E2%80%9Cmisconduct%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20no-confidence%20motion%20was%20ultimately%20defeated%20by%20a%20voice%20vote%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20the%20opposition%20MPs%20in%20the%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBarely%20ten%20minutes%20on%20Manipur%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20began%20speaking%20at%205%20pm%2C%20he%20first%20mentioned%20Manipur%20only%20at%206.42%20pm%20as%20opposition%20MPs%20started%20walking%20out%20of%20the%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYesterday%2C%20Amit%20%3Cem%3Ebhai%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Shah)%20said%20that%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-court-manipur-hc-meitei-scheduled-tribes-list%5C%22%3Eorder%20came%20from%20the%20high%20court%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20Manipur%2C%20which%20saw%20a%20sequence%20of%20events%20that%20led%20to%20violence%20in%20the%20state.%20Many%20families%20lost%20their%20loved%20ones.%20Terrible%20crimes%20were%20committed%20against%20women%20and%20this%20is%20condemnable%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTo%20punish%20the%20perpetrators%20both%20central%20and%20state%20governments%20are%20trying%20their%20best.%20I%20want%20to%20assure%20all%20citizens%20that%20all%20our%20efforts%20are%20underway%20and%20peace%20will%20soon%20be%20restored.%20Manipur%20will%20move%20forward%20with%20new%20%3Cem%3Eatma%20vishwas%20(%3C%2Fem%3Eself%20confidence)%20towards%20development%20soon.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20also%20want%20to%20tell%20the%20people%20of%20Manipur%2C%20to%20the%20women%2C%20daughters%20and%20sisters%20that%20the%20country%20is%20with%20you%20and%20this%20House%20is%20with%20you.%20Together%20we%20will%20confront%20this%20challenge%20and%20bring%20back%20peace.%20I%20want%20to%20tell%20Manipur%20that%20we%20are%20trying%20our%20best%20to%20ensure%20Manipur%20moves%20towards%20peace%20soon%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Flok-sabha-debates-no-confidence-motion-even-as-pm-modi-absent%5C%22%3Eno%20confidence%20motion%20debate%20began%20on%20Tuesday%20(August%208)%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Modi%20only%20appeared%20in%20the%20House%20for%20the%20first%20time%20on%20Thursday%20afternoon%20%E2%80%93%20first%2C%20briefly%20during%20Chowdhury%E2%80%99s%20speech%2C%20and%20later%2C%20just%20before%20he%20was%20due%20to%20give%20his%20reply%20shortly%20before%205%20pm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20in%20his%20brief%20comments%20on%20Manipur%2C%20Modi%20took%20aim%20at%20the%20opposition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20they%20had%20agreed%20to%20Shah%E2%80%99s%20requests%2C%20we%20could%20have%20had%20a%20good%20discussion.%20Shah%20gave%20a%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Famit-shah-defends-biren-singh-in-parliament%5C%22%3E%20detailed%20statement%20%3C%2Fa%3Eyesterday%20and%20the%20country%20was%20shocked%20by%20the%20lies%20spread%20by%20the%20opposition%20about%20the%20situation%20in%20Manipur%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20said%20come%20and%20discuss%20Manipur%2C%20the%20home%20minister%20even%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fparliament-shah-writes-manipur-opposition-mps-pm-statement%5C%22%3Ewrote%20a%20letter%3C%2Fa%3E.%20But%20they%20had%20no%20intention%20or%20courage..%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%20said%20that%20Shah%E2%80%99s%20speech%20on%20Wednesday%20continued%20for%20over%20two%20hours%20and%20was%20a%20detailed%20reply%20on%20Manipur%20%E2%80%9Cwithout%20any%20politics%E2%80%9D%20that%20took%20into%20account%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20concerns%20of%20the%20citizens%20and%20the%20government%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20purpose%20%5Bof%20the%20speech%5D%20was%20also%20to%20make%20the%20people%20aware%20and%20send%20a%20message%20of%20peace%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%20also%20said%20that%20as%20Shah%20explained%20the%20day%20before%2C%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20problems%20have%20not%20developed%20over%20the%20last%20few%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CManipur%E2%80%99s%20problems%20are%20being%20presented%20as%20if%20these%20problems%20have%20started%20recently.%20As%20Shah%20explained%20extensively%20yesterday%20%E2%80%93%20the%20genesis%20of%20problems%20in%20the%20Northeast%20is%20Congress.%20It%20is%20not%20the%20people%20of%20the%20North%20East%20but%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20politics%20that%20is%20responsible%20for%20this%20(situation)%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20prime%20minister%20also%20said%20that%20the%20previous%20Congress%20governments%20did%20little%20for%20the%20Northeast.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20(Congress)%20have%20never%20tried%20to%20understand%20the%20emotions%20of%20the%20Northeast%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20visited%20(Northeast)%2050%20times.%20This%20is%20not%20just%20data%2C%20this%20is%20dedication%20towards%20Northeast.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWho%E2%80%99s%20government%20was%20there%20in%20Manipur%20when%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20picture%20was%20not%20allowed%20in%20government%20offices%2C%20whose%20government%20was%20there%20in%20Manipur%20when%20the%20decision%20to%20not%20allow%20the%20national%20anthem%20in%20schools%20was%20taken%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccusing%20the%20opposition%20of%20%E2%80%9Cselective%E2%80%9D%20outrage%2C%20Modi%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThey%20cannot%20think%20beyond%20politics.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20opposition%20staged%20a%20walkout%20at%20around%206.40%20pm%20(about%20an%20hour%20and%2040%20minutes%20into%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20speech)%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%20accused%20them%20of%20not%20being%20ready%20to%20listen%20to%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThose%20who%20don%E2%80%99t%20believe%20in%20democracy%20are%20ready%20to%20speak%20but%20not%20listen.%20If%20you%20speak%20the%20truth%20they%20leave.%20They%20throw%20garbage%20and%20run%20away%2C%20they%20spread%20lies%20and%20run%20away.%20The%20country%20has%20no%20hopes%20from%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98The%20Congress%20divided%20India%20into%20three%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHitting%20out%20at%20Congress%20MP%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Frahul-gandhi-parliament-bharat-mata-manipur%5C%22%3ERahul%20Gandhi%2C%20who%20on%20Wednesday%20accused%20Modi%20of%20%E2%80%9Cmurdering%20Bharat%20Mata%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Manipur%E2%80%9D%2C%20Modi%20said%20that%20his%20words%20had%20hurt%20every%20Indian.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C(Those)%20words%20on%20Bharat%20Mata%20have%20hurt%20every%20Indian%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20what%20has%20happened%E2%80%A6without%20power%20some%20people%20cannot%20live.%20What%20kind%20of%20a%20language%20is%20this%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThese%20people%20talk%20about%20murdering%20the%20constitution.%20Have%20they%20forgotten%20August%2014%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20asked%2C%20referring%20to%20India%E2%80%99s%20partition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20still%20living%20with%20that%20pain.%20The%20same%20people%20who%20divided%20Ma%20Bharat%20into%20three%20pieces%2C%20when%20they%20had%20to%20make%20our%20country%20independent%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECongress%20likes%20dynasty%20politics%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%20said%20that%20the%20Congress%20has%20always%20favoured%20dynastic%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20always%20opposed%20dynastic%20politics%20but%20the%20Congress%20likes%20%3Cem%3Eparivarvaad%2C%20durbaarbaad%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%20said%20that%20because%20of%20dynastic%20politics%2C%20the%20rights%20of%20leaders%20like%20B.R.%20Ambedkar%2C%20Babu%20Jagjivan%20Ram%2C%20Morarji%20Desai%2C%20Charan%20Singh%20were%20taken%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaking%20aim%20at%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20speech%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20where%20he%20said%20that%20Lanka%20was%20not%20set%20ablaze%20by%20Hanuman%20but%20by%20his%20arrogance%2C%20Modi%20agreed%20that%20that%20was%20true.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20true%2C%20that%20is%20why%20the%20people%20of%20this%20country%20have%20behaved%20like%20Ram%20and%20ended%20that%20arrogance.%20From%20400%20seats%20they%20are%20now%20down%20to%2040%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20truth%20is%20the%20people%20of%20this%20country%20have%20given%20full%20majority%20to%20this%20government%20twice.%20But%20their%20problem%20is%20%E2%80%93%20how%20can%20a%20%3Cem%3Egareeb%20ka%20beta%20(%3C%2Fem%3Eson%20of%20a%20poor%20man)%20sit%20here.%20You%20thought%20this%20seat%20was%20your%20dynastic%20right.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20end%20they%20are%20%3Cem%3Enaamdar%3C%2Fem%3E%20(dynast)%20and%20we%20are%20%3Cem%3Ekaamdar%20%3C%2Fem%3E(those%20known%20by%20their%20work)%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbjp-usual-script-politics-redfined%5C%22%3EWith%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Usual%20Script%20Appearing%20to%20Fall%20Short%2C%20Politics%20Is%20Set%20to%20Be%20Redefined%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Changing%20name%20to%20INDIA%20won%E2%80%99t%20change%20your%20fortunes%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHitting%20out%20at%20the%20opposition%20INDIA%20bloc%2C%20Modi%20said%20that%20changing%20their%20name%20from%20UPA%20to%20INDIA%20will%20not%20change%20their%20fortunes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20feel%20that%20by%20changing%20their%20alliance%E2%80%99s%20name%20to%20INDIA%20they%20will%20rule%20the%20country.%20But%20this%20is%20a%20%3Cem%3Eghamandiya%3C%2Fem%3E%20(arrogant)%20alliance%20and%20I%20want%20to%20tell%20them%20that%20by%20changing%20your%20name%20you%20cannot%20change%20your%20fortunes%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20the%20name%20INDIA%20was%20also%20decided%20by%20taking%20the%20NDA%E2%80%99s%20help%20and%20%5Bthat%20it%5D%20defined%20corruption.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20order%20to%20keep%20themselves%20alive%20they%20had%20to%20take%20the%20NDA%E2%80%99s%20help%20in%20naming%20their%20alliance.%20But%20their%20arrogance%20does%20not%20leave%20them%2C%20so%20they%20had%20to%20add%20to%20I%E2%80%99s%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20first%20I%20(in%20INDIA)%20stands%20for%20the%20arrogance%20of%2025%20parties%20and%20the%20other%20I%20for%20one%20family%E2%80%99s%20arrogance.%20They%20stole%20NDA%20from%20NDA%20and%20divided%20INDIA%20with%20I%20dot%20N%20dot%20D%20dot%20I%20dot%20A%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Frahul-gandhi-matters-to-the-bjp-because-he-targets-its-soft-spots-nationalism-incorruptibility%5C%22%3ERahul%20Gandhi%20Matters%20to%20the%20BJP%20Because%20He%20Targets%20Its%20Soft%20Spots%20%E2%80%93%20Nationalism%2C%20Incorruptibility%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndia%20will%20become%20the%20third%20largest%20economy%20in%20the%20world%20by%20next%20no-confidence%20motion%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%20said%20that%20like%20he%20had%20promised%20in%202018%2C%20during%20the%20previous%20no-confidence%20motion%20that%20was%20moved%20against%20his%20government%2C%20that%20another%20motion%20will%20come%20in%202023%2C%20a%20third%20motion%20will%20come%20in%202028.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20had%20promised%20in%202018%20that%20they%20will%20bring%20a%20no-confidence%20motion%20again%20in%202023%20and%20they%20have%20done%20so%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CUnder%20the%20Congress%2C%20the%20Indian%20economy%20was%20at%20the%2010th%2C%2011th%20and%2012th%20spot%20in%20the%20world.%20After%202014%20it%20is%20now%20among%20the%20top%20five%20economies%20in%20the%20world.%20When%20you%20bring%20the%20next%20no-confidence%20motion%20in%202028%20India%20will%20be%20the%20third%20largest%20economy%20in%20the%20world%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%20also%20listed%20his%20government%E2%80%99s%20achievements%20in%20the%20last%20nine%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWHO%20said%20the%20Swachh%20Bharat%20Mission%20saved%20the%20lives%20of%203%20lakh%20people.%20UNICEF%20said%20that%20the%20poor%20are%20saving%20Rs%2050%2C000%20every%20year%20because%20of%20this%20%5Bmission%5D.%20But%20the%20Congress%20and%20other%20Opposition%20parties%20don%E2%80%99t%20believe%20it.%20What%20the%20world%20sees%2C%20these%20people%20refuse%20to%20acknowledge%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%20also%20thanked%20the%20opposition%20for%20moving%20the%20no-confidence%20motion%2C%20so%20he%20could%20give%20a%20detailed%20list%20of%20his%20government%E2%80%99s%20work%20to%20the%20people%20of%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98PM%20absolved%20himself%20of%20all%20responsibility%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20opposition%20that%20staged%20a%20walkout%20after%20an%20hour%20and%2040%20minutes%20said%20that%20they%20took%20the%20step%20as%20Modi%20was%20giving%20a%20political%20speech%20and%20not%20talking%20about%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3Edeputy%20leader%20of%20the%20Congress%20in%20the%20house%2C%20Gaurav%20Gogoi%2C%20who%20had%20moved%20the%20motion%20last%20month%2C%20said%20that%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20decided%20to%20walk%20out%20because%20the%20prime%20minister%20absolved%20himself%20of%20all%20responsibility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20prime%20minister%20absolved%20his%20government%20%E2%80%93%20at%20the%20centre%20and%20the%20state%20%E2%80%93%20of%20all%20failures%20in%20Manipur%20and%20did%20not%20take%20any%20responsibility%20for%20the%20violence%20and%20rapes%20in%20Manipur.%20It%20seems%20they%20want%20a%20divided%20Manipur%20and%20the%20nexus%20of%20the%20drug%20mafia%20with%20the%20chief%20minister%20(N.%20Biren%20Singh)%20will%20continue.%20He%20also%20avoided%20answers%20on%20key%20issues%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Findias-workforce-not-rising-quality-of-jobs-very-low-cmies-mahesh-vyas%5C%22%3Eunemployment%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Findia-china-sco-g20%5C%22%3EChina%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20remarks%20made%20on%20Pulwama%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fsatya-pal-malik-full-interview-pulwama-modi%5C%22%3Eformer%20J%26amp%3BK%20governor%20Satyapal%20Malik%3C%2Fa%3E.%20For%20all%20these%20reasons%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20decided%20to%20stage%20a%20walkout.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20about%20the%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20focus%20on%20his%20government%E2%80%99s%20achievements%20instead%20of%20Manipur%2C%20Gogoi%20said%20that%20Modi%20had%20no%20answers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20prime%20minister%20did%20not%20have%20answers%20on%20the%20three%20questions%20I%20raised%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20about%20why%20he%20didn%E2%80%99t%20go%20to%20Manipur%2C%20why%20he%20was%20silent%20for%2080%20days%2C%20and%20why%20he%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20sacked%20the%20chief%20minister.%20He%20only%20tried%20to%20overrule%20us%20by%20bureaucratic%20achievements%20of%20his%20government%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnarendra-modi-talked-about-the-manipur-violence-but-did-he-really%5C%22%3ENarendra%20Modi%20Talked%20About%20the%20Manipur%20Violence.%20But%20Did%20He%20Really%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELeader%20of%20Congress%20suspended%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%E2%80%99s%20speech%20also%20saw%20Chowdhury%E2%80%99s%20suspension%20for%20%E2%80%9Cmisconduct%E2%80%9D%20after%20Union%20minister%20for%20parliamentary%20affairs%20Pralhad%20Joshi%20moved%20a%20motion%20against%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJoshi%20moved%20a%20motion%20%E2%80%9Cthat%20this%20House%20having%20taken%20the%20serious%20note%20of%20the%20gross%2C%20deliberate%20and%20repeated%20misconduct%20of%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Chowdhury%20in%20utter%20disregard%20to%20the%20House%20and%20authority%20of%20Chair%20resolve%20that%20the%20matter%20of%20his%20misconduct%20be%20referred%20to%20Committee%20of%20Privileges%20of%20the%20House%20for%20further%20investigation%20and%20reported%20to%20the%20House%2C%20and%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Chowdhury%20be%20suspended%20from%20the%20service%20of%20the%20House%20till%20the%20Committee%20submits%20its%20report.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20during%20his%20speech%2C%20Chowdhury%20had%20criticised%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20silence%20on%20Manipur%20and%20compared%20the%20prime%20minister%20with%20Nirav%20Modi%20and%20said%20that%20when%20he%20saw%20that%20the%20fugitive%20businessman%20was%20in%20the%20Caribbean%20he%20felt%20relieved.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20thought%20Nirav%20Modi%20has%20left%20India%20and%20gone%20far%20away%20but%20now%20I%20know%20Nirav%20Modi%20has%20not%20gone%20far%20away%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20compared%20Modi%20to%20Dhritarashtra%20and%20said%20when%20Draupadi%20was%20disrobed%20Dhritarashtra%20%E2%80%9Cwas%20blind%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20no%20difference%20between%20Manipur%20and%20Hastinapur%20Dhritarashtra%20is%20still%20blind.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20remarks%20were%20expunged%20after%20protests%20from%20the%20treasury%20benches%20who%20demanded%20an%20apology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20speech%20as%20well%2C%20Chowdhury%20led%20several%20interruptions%20demanding%20that%20he%20address%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691684667000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F10214946%2Fimage-1211.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnarendra-modi-parliament-speech-manipur%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Opposition%20leaders%2C%20who%20had%20urged%20PM%20Modi%20to%20address%20the%20three-month-long%20violence%20during%20the%20entire%20parliamentary%20session%2C%20staged%20a%20walkout%20when%2C%20after%201%20hour%20and%2040%20minutes%20of%20the%20speech%2C%20there%20was%20no%20mention%20of%20Manipur.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%