eam%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20inspired%20by%20a%20Georgian%20recipe.%20The%20announcement%20of%20the%20flavour%20mentions%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D6z-pIgKG27M%5C%22%3Eseveral%20more%20outlandish%20Georgian%20flavours%3C%2Fa%3E%20trialled%20by%20English%20Heritage%20before%20it%20landed%20on%20brown%20bread%2C%20such%20as%20Parmesan%20and%20cucumber.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEnglish%20Heritage%20is%20not%20alone%20in%20its%20efforts%20to%20beguile%20visitors%20with%20historical%20treats.%20In%20Edinburgh%2C%20the%20National%20Trust%20for%20Scotland%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nts.org.uk%2Fvisit%2Fplaces%2Fgladstones-land%2Fhistory-of-food-and-drink%5C%22%3EGladstone%E2%80%99s%20Land%3C%2Fa%3E%20features%20an%20ice%20cream%20parlour%20linked%20to%20the%20dairy%20which%20stood%20there%20in%201904.%20The%20property%20sells%20elderflower%20and%20lemon%20curd%20ice%20cream%20based%20on%20a%20recipe%20from%201770%2C%20and%20visitors%20can%20go%20on%20several%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nts.org.uk%2Fvisit%2Fplaces%2Fgladstones-land%2Fhighlights%2Ftours%5C%22%3Efood-themed%20tours%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20brown%20bread%20ice%20cream%2C%20praised%20for%20its%20caramel%20nuttiness%2C%20may%20be%20a%20more%20familiar%20flavour%20to%20contemporary%20eaters%20than%20other%20historical%20offerings%2C%20the%20iced%20delights%20eaten%20in%20Britain%20in%20previous%20centuries%20took%20a%20huge%20variety%20of%20flavours%20and%20forms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.canalmuseum.org.uk%2Fice%2Fmarshall.htm%5C%22%3EAgnes%20Marshall%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20authority%20on%20ice%20cream%20during%20the%20late%2019th%20century%2C%20published%20two%20cookbooks%20specifically%20about%20%E2%80%9Cices%E2%80%9D%20(1885)%20and%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.canalmuseum.org.uk%2Fice%2Fmarshall.htm%5C%22%3EFancy%20Ices%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%20(1894).%20They%20included%20flavours%20from%20an%20elaborately%20moulded%20and%20coloured%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farchive.org%2Fdetails%2Fb21528068%2Fpage%2F42%2Fmode%2F2up%3Fq%3Dspinach%5C%22%3Eiced%20spinach%20%C3%A0%20la%20cr%C3%A8me%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farchive.org%2Fdetails%2Fb29314501%2Fpage%2F130%2Fmode%2F2up%5C%22%3Elittle%20devilled%20ices%20in%20cups%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20latter%20consisted%20of%20a%20chicken%20p%C3%A2t%C3%A9%20spiked%20with%20curry%20powder%20and%20Worcestershire%20sauce%2C%20egg%20yolks%20and%20anchovies%2C%20which%20was%20then%20mixed%20with%20gravy%2C%20gelatine%20and%20whipped%20cream%2C%20before%20being%20frozen%20in%20decorative%20cups%20and%20served%20%E2%80%9Cfor%20a%20luncheon%20or%20second-course%20dish%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F10194606%2FFancy_Ices_ice_cream_illustration.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22747%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F10194606%2FFancy_Ices_ice_cream_illustration.jpg%20747w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F10194606%2FFancy_Ices_ice_cream_illustration-187x300.jpg%20187w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F10194606%2FFancy_Ices_ice_cream_illustration-637x1024.jpg%20637w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-667547%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%20of%20different%20ice%20cream%20designs%20made%20by%20Agnes%20B.%20Marshall%20using%20moulds%20from%20her%201894%20book%20%E2%80%98Fancy%20Ices%E2%80%99.%20Photo%3A%20Wikipedia%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20texts%20contain%20even%20more%20outlandish%20flavours%20alongside%20the%20typical%2C%20sweet%20offerings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrench%20foodie%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fprogrammes%2Farticles%2F5cSf963VtsNDsr3qj0qCVNV%2F8-scoops-on-the-history-of-ice-cream%5C%22%3EMonsieur%20Emy%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsotherans.co.uk%2Fproducts%2Femy-m-lart-de-bien-faire-les-glaces-doffice-ou-les-vrais-principes-pour-congeler-tous-les-raffrichemens-la-manier%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EL%E2%80%99Art%20de%20Bien%20Faire%20les%20Glaces%20d%E2%80%99Office%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20(1768)%20has%20recipes%20for%20truffle%2C%20saffron%20and%20various%20cheese-flavoured%20ice%20creams.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20history%20of%20ice%20cream%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20time%20Marshall%20was%20publishing%2C%20ice%20cream%20was%20far%20more%20accessible%20to%20the%20public%20than%20in%20earlier%20centuries.%20Prior%20to%20the%201800s%2C%20ice%20was%20collected%20from%20frozen%20waterways%20and%20stored%20in%20underground%20ice%20houses%2C%20largely%20restricted%20to%20large%20estates%20with%20the%20necessary%20land%2C%20wealth%20and%20resources.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20the%201820s%2C%20however%2C%20ice%20was%20imported%20to%20Britain%20from%20Europe%20and%20then%20the%20US%20and%20stored%20in%20ice%20wells%20and%20warehouses.%20The%20importation%20of%20larger%20stocks%20of%20ice%20reduced%20costs%2C%20while%20simultaneously%2C%20innovators%20were%20designing%20apparatus%20for%20mechanical%20freezing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20547px)%2085vw%2C%20547px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F10195244%2Fimage-1209.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22547%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F10195244%2Fimage-1209.png%20547w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F10195244%2Fimage-1209-188x300.png%20188w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-667548%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22872%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EAn%20advertisement%20for%20Marshall%E2%80%99s%20patent%20freezer%20from%201885.%20Photo%3A%20Wikimedia%20Commons%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20would%20be%20a%20long%20time%20until%20ice%20was%20easily%20produced%20within%20the%20home%2C%20but%20cheaper%20ice%20made%20ice%20cream%20more%20readily%20available%20and%20implements%20were%20devised%20so%20it%20could%20be%20made%20at%20home.%20Both%20Emy%20and%20Marshall%E2%80%99s%20cookbooks%20depicting%20ice%20cream%20makers%20and%20Marshall%E2%80%99s%20patent%20freezer%20enlisted%20the%20same%20freezing%20technique%20as%20Emy%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vam.ac.uk%2Fblog%2Fcreating-new-europe-1600-1800-galleries%2Fcan-i-have-a-taste-of-your-ice-cream%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESarbotiere%20et%20son%20Seau%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fresearch.colonialwilliamsburg.org%2FFoundation%2Fjournal%2FSpring10%2Ficecream.cfm%5C%22%3Epot%20freezer%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20bucket).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIce%20and%20salt%20were%20placed%20around%20a%20bucket%2C%20within%20which%20a%20custard%20or%20water%20mixture%20was%20stirred%20or%20rotated%20until%20it%20froze.%20Marshall%E2%80%99s%20innovation%20was%20the%20shallow%20pan%2C%20which%20gave%20an%20increased%20surface%20area%20for%20faster%20freezing.%20Equipped%20with%20such%20a%20freezer%20(and%20perhaps%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farchive.org%2Fdetails%2Fb29314501%2Fpage%2F246%2Fmode%2F2up%5C%22%3EMarshall%E2%80%99s%20patent%20Ice%20Cave%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20for%20storing%20the%20ices)%2C%20middle-class%20housewives%20could%20produce%20ice%20cream%20in%20their%20own%20kitchens.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIce%20cream%20and%20leisure%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIce%20cream%20is%20well-suited%20for%20engaging%20visitors%20at%20heritage%20properties%20today%2C%20not%20because%20of%20the%20history%20of%20how%20it%20was%20produced%20within%20the%20home%20but%20because%20of%20its%20holiday%20connotations.%20Whether%20it%20is%20a%20%E2%80%9C99%E2%80%9D%2C%20an%20%E2%80%9Coyster%E2%80%9D%20enjoyed%20at%20the%20beach%2C%20or%20the%20nearing%20jingle%20of%20an%20ice%20cream%20truck%2C%20ice%20cream%20has%20clear%20cultural%20and%20emotional%20links%20to%20recreation%20and%20enjoyment.%20This%20was%20also%20true%20in%20the%20past.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%2019th%20century%20Britain%2C%20street%20vendors%20(many%20of%20them%20Italian%20immigrants)%20began%20selling%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscarboroughmuseumsandgalleries.org.uk%2Fobject%2Fpenny-lick-glasses%2F%5C%22%3Epenny%20licks%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20%E2%80%9Chokey-pokey%E2%80%9D%20from%20stalls%20or%20carts%20in%20the%20streets.%20In%20contrast%20to%20the%20immaculately%20moulded%20delicacies%20in%20Marshall%E2%80%99s%20cookbook%20%E2%80%93%20which%20required%20the%20purchase%20of%20several%20pieces%20of%20equipment%20%E2%80%93%20this%20ice%20cream%20was%20to%20be%20enjoyed%20while%20out%20and%20about.%20It%20was%20also%20cheap%2C%20as%20implied%20by%20%E2%80%9Cpenny%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20title.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECustomers%20would%20purchase%20their%20ice%20upon%20a%20glass%20%E2%80%9Click%E2%80%9D%2C%20eat%20it%20and%20then%20return%20the%20lick%20to%20the%20vendor%20for%20reuse.%20With%20growing%20numbers%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fhistory%2Fbritish%2Fvictorians%2Fseaside_01.shtml%23%3A%257E%3Atext%3DMost%2520of%2520our%2C%2527traditional%2527%2520summer%2520holiday.%5C%22%3Eseaside%20resorts%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20rise%20of%20the%20leisure%20industry%20over%20the%2019th%20century%2C%20ices%20were%20enjoyed%20while%20on%20holiday%20or%20daily%20excursions%20and%20at%20public%20events%20like%20exhibitions%20or%20fairs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F10200540%2Fimage-1210.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22920%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F10200540%2Fimage-1210.png%20920w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F10200540%2Fimage-1210-300x189.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-667552%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22580%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EChildren%20surround%20an%20ice%20cream%20vendor%20in%201909.%20Photo%3A%20Wikimedia%20Commons%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20the%20portability%20of%20ice%20cream%2C%20as%20well%20as%20its%20culinary%20appeal%2C%20that%20has%20led%20to%20its%20lasting%20place%20in%20our%20leisure%20time%20%E2%80%93%20a%20delicious%20treat%20that%20can%20be%20enjoyed%2C%20one-handed%2C%20as%20part%20of%20a%20larger%20experience.%20The%20act%20of%20eating%20ice%20cream%20prepared%20from%20a%20Georgian%20or%20Victorian%20recipe%20therefore%20connects%20today%E2%80%99s%20visitors%20to%20a%20long%20tradition%20of%20enjoying%20ices%20recreationally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20heritage%20properties%20are%20unlikely%20to%20embrace%20the%20more%20unsanitary%20ways%20ice%20cream%20used%20to%20be%20eaten%2C%20serving%20up%20historical%20recipes%20gives%20visitors%20a%20chance%20to%20savour%20a%20new%20sensory%20layer%20of%20the%20past.%20That%20taste%20can%20be%20linked%20into%20larger%20histories.%20From%20ice%20cream%2C%20we%20can%20learn%20about%20technological%20developments%2C%20changing%20attitudes%20towards%20sanitation%2C%20global%20travel%2C%20the%20availability%20of%20ingredients%20throughout%20time%2C%20trends%2C%20fashion%20and%20leisure%20habits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelving%20into%20the%20history%20of%20food%20%E2%80%93%20from%20the%20tins%20in%20our%20cupboards%2C%20to%20a%20cup%20of%20tea%2C%20or%20an%20ice%20cream%20at