s%2F2023%2F08%2Fignis-careers-1691584663-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fignis-careers-1691584663-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fignis-careers-1691584663-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-326820%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ERennis%20charges%20up%20to%20Rs%20700%20per%20student%20per%20year%20from%20low-cost%20private%20schools.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20this%2C%20Rennis%20says%20a%20trainer%20is%20sent%20to%20a%20school%20once%20every%20week%20and%20is%20provided%20with%20a%20unit-wise%20printed%20textbook%20with%20creative%20ways%20to%20teach%20the%20children.%20In%20conversation%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%2C%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ENarmada%20Samala%2C%20a%20rural%20teacher%20fellow%20in%20a%20school%20in%20Khammam%20district%20of%20Telangana%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CTeachers%20are%20trained%20to%20develop%20their%20skills%20so%20that%20they%20can%20train%20students%20accordingly.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20what%20makes%20the%20teaching%20method%20unique%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CIf%20I%20have%20to%20teach%20students%20about%20prepositions%2C%20I%20won%E2%80%99t%20start%20by%20teaching%20them%20the%20definition%20and%20what%20are%20the%20words%20of%20prepositions%20on%20board.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHere%2C%20a%20teacher%20hides%20any%20object%20in%20the%20classroom%2C%20and%20students%20are%20asked%20if%20it%20is%20%E2%80%98under%E2%80%99%20the%20table%20or%20is%20it%20%E2%80%98in%E2%80%99%20the%20bag.%20After%20the%20activities%2C%20we%20tell%20the%20students%20that%20the%20words%20they%20used%20like%2C%20%E2%80%98in%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98under%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98on%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98behind%E2%80%99%2C%20or%20%E2%80%98beside%E2%80%99%2C%20are%20called%20prepositions.%20So%2C%20they%20easil