%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20does%20good%20counselling%20mean%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Rohini%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CTrust%20is%20essential%20and%20that%20is%20built%20by%20being%20authentic%2C%20empathetic%20and%20non-judgmental.%20An%20effective%20counsellor%20will%20listen%20to%20you%20with%20understanding%20and%20compassion%20and%20without%20assuming%20or%20lecturing.%20They%20will%20help%20you%20to%20understand%20your%20own%20thoughts%20and%20feelings%2C%20and%20support%20you%20as%20you%20work%20through%20your%20issues.%20Being%20in%20therapy%20is%20hard%20because%20most%20of%20us%20are%20not%20comfortable%20with%20our%20own%20vulnerability.%20Therefore%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20imperative%20for%20a%20counsellor%20to%20never%20trivialise%20a%20patient%20or%20client%E2%80%99s%20concerns%20and%20abuse%20their%20vulnerability.%20Our%20task%20is%20to%20ensure%20that%20they%20feel%20comfortable%20enough%20to%20embark%20on%20this%20journey%20of%20healing.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaman%20(name%20changed)%20was%2019%2C%20struggling%20with%20severe%20depression%2C%20anxiety%20and%20%E2%80%98self-harming%20tendencies%E2%80%99%20when%20he%20discovered%20The%20Able%20Mind%20last%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWith%20my%20first%20interaction%20with%20The%20Able%20Mind%2C%20I%20was%20immediately%20embraced%20by%20a%20wave%20of%20understanding%20and%20support.%20She%20(Rohini%20Rajeev)%20has%20ensured%20that%20I%20receive%20the%20best%20possible%20care%20by%20connecting%20me%20with%20a%20highly%20competent%20psychiatrist%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCmvxqXtsAoX%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instag