%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D326524%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sri%20Harsha%2C%20along%20with%20Sharath%20Chandra%20and%20Nirali%20Parikh%2C%20co-founded%20%E2%80%98Hypothalamus%E2%80%99%20to%20address%20the%20healthcare%20gap%20in%20the%20food%20industry.%20They%20provide%20health-focused%20meal%20delivery%20service%20for%20patients%20with%20cancer%2C%20diabetes%2C%20PCOS%2C%20etc.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F326524%2Ffood-for-patiets-of-diabetes-cancer-pcos-home-delivery-hypothalamus-mumbai%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%20To%20Do%20For%20Injured%20Animals%20on%20Streets%3F%20One%20MBA%20Grad%20Has%20Saved%2040000%20Strays%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETrigger%20warning%3A%20Animal%20abuse%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAditi%20Nair%20has%20been%20able%20to%20do%20what%20many%20of%20us%20can%20only%20dream%20of%20%E2%80%94%20marrying%20her%20passion%20and%20profession.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202010%2C%20while%20she%20was%20pursuing%20her%20MBA%20degree%2C%20she%20was%20challenged%20by%20her%20professor%20to%20find%20something%20she%20was%20passionate%20about.%20She%20recalls%2C%20%E2%80%9CDr%20Kaustubh%20Dhargalkar%2C%20who%20is%20also%20my%20mentor%2C%20would%20always%20ask%20me%20to%20look%20for%20my%20passion%20and%20what%20I%20could%20do%20about%20it.%20Meanwhile%2C%20I%20was%20deeply%20interested%20in%20animal%20welfare.%20However%2C%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20how%20I%20could%20actually%20help%20animals.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20find%20her%20answer%2C%20she%20set%20out%20on%20a%20journey%20across%20the%20country.%20In%20April%20that%20year%2C%20she%20began%20volunteering%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F316625%2Fruvuotuo-belho-builds-mini-zoo-in-kohima-nagaland-saves-birds-an