s%2F2023%2F08%2Fkavi-2-1691153952.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Madhuri%20collects%20bottles%20from%20customers%20and%20ragpickers%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fkavi-2-1691153952.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fkavi-2-1691153952-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fkavi-2-1691153952-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fkavi-2-1691153952-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fkavi-2-1691153952-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-326398%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThey%20collect%20glass%20bottles%20and%20convert%20them%20into%20serving%20sets%2C%20platters%2C%20lamps%20etc%3B%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Madhuri%20Balodi%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20adds%20that%20they%20focus%20on%20the%20finishing%20touches%20very%20carefully%20so%20the%20products%20don%E2%80%99t%20feel%20upcycled%2C%20but%20rather%20feel%20brand%20new!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20social%20media%20campaigns%20also%20resulted%20in%20something%20very%20sweet%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20remarks.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20people%20came%20to%20us%20with%20their%20bottles%2C%20many%20shared%20special%20stories%20behind%20each%20of%20them!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20people%20saying%20things%20like%20%E2%80%98I%20opened%20this%20bottle%20when%20my%20daughter%20was%20born%E2%80%99%20or%20%E2%80%98My%20best%20friend%20gifted%20me%20this%20bottle%2020%20years%20ago%E2%80%99.%20They%20come%20to%20us%20with%20requests%20to%20save%20the%20bottles%20and%20preserve%20them%20in%20a%20memorable%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMadhuri%20and%20Amit%20share%20that%20such%20requests%20and%20stories%20make%2