%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9CFinding%20big%20players%20in%20India%20in%20this%20segment%20was%20difficult.%20In%20China%2C%20a%20sugarcane%20bagasse%20factory%20has%20a%20capacity%20of%20150-200%20tonnes%20per%20day%2C%20while%20in%20India%20it%E2%80%99s%20just%20two%20tonnes.%20The%20scale%20difference%20is%20huge.%20We%20had%20to%20work%20on%20scaling%20up%2C%20which%20we%20did.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20built%20a%20large%20factory%20for%20producing%20palm%20leaf%20plates%20in%20Tumakuru%2C%20Karnataka.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20were%20small%20cottage%20industries%20in%20the%20palm%20leaf%20segment.%20So%20we%20worked%20with%20the%20Krishikalpa%20Foundation%20to%20build%20a%20large%20factory.%20Farmers%20from%2021%20districts%20came%20together%20and%20built%20a%20factory%20which%20has%2045%20machines%20today.%20All%20the%20products%20are%20exported%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20June%202021%2C%20they%20started%20selling%20six%20products%2C%20including%20palm%20leaf%20plates%20and%20bamboo-based%20cutlery%20online%20in%20North%20America.%20They%20replaced%20plastic%20in%20everyday%20products%2C%20such%20as%20forks%2C%20spoons%2C%20cups%2C%20straws%2C%20plates%20etc.%20They%20also%20replaced%20paper%20with%20their%20compostable%20paper%20towels%2C%20which%20are%20actually%20made%20out%20of%20bamboo.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20use%20agro-waste%20to%20make%20our%20products.%20We%20work%20with%20sugarcane%20bagasse%2C%20rice%20khus%2C%20wheat%20khus%2C%20and%20palm%20leaves.%20We%20also%20don%E2%80%99t%20cut%20any%20trees%20to%20make%20our%20products.%20All%20our%20finished%20products%20are%20replacements%20for%20single-use%20plastics%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Rahul%2C%20adding%20that%20all%20their%20products%20are%20%E2%80%9Cearthworm%20certified.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSince%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20use%20plastic%20or%20cut%20trees%2C%20all%20our%20products%20are%20compostable.%20It%E2%80%99s%20goo